e.co.uk/tag/amazon\"\u003eAmazon\u003c/a\u003e buy, but that is even cheaper than Aldi’s version. Now Lidl is trumping them both, and I’m pleased to say the Lidl Grillmeister Ceramic Barbecue doesn’t scrimp on features.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe compact BBQ is designed for smoking, searing, baking, grilling and high-temperature cooking, with its ceramic shell carefully designed to retain temperatures up to 450 degrees. It also comes with an integrated thermometer, so you can ensure your food is cooked at the perfect temperature.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe BBQ is 26.5cm or 10.4” inches in diameter, making it slightly smaller in diameter than The Big Green Egg MiniMax, which is 33cm or 13” in diameter. This is a great size for couples looking to grill this summer, or groups of two to four. Because of this, if you’re looking to host larger groups of people, I’d suggest investing in one of the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/outdoor-living/best-gas-bbq\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/outdoor-living/best-gas-bbq\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ebest gas BBQs\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, such as the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2Fdp%2FB071S5NY9Y%3Ftag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Didealhome-gb-3082002987420349492-21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B071S5NY9Y\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2Fdp%2FB071S5NY9Y%3Ftag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Dhawk-custom-tracking-21\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Amazon UK\" data-merchant-id=\"1027\" data-merchant-network=\"Amazonuk\" data-merchant-url=\"amazon.co.uk\"\u003e\u003cu\u003eChar-Broil Gas BBQ (£629.99 at Amazon)\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, which has an enormous amount of cooking space, making it an excellent addition to any garden party.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ.png\" alt=\"Grillmeister Ceramic Barbecue on pink background.\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X8A5VUtU2GwL388StDALNQ.png\"/\u003e\u003c/pi